    <accessrestrict id="aspace_hzc212408n506as97071255607225">
      <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
      <p>The Archives of American art does not own the original papers. Use is limited to the microfilm copy.</p>
    </accessrestrict>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc212408n520as29530343605034">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Register of paintings, 1801-1871 (1 v., 139 p.); Sully's hints for pictures, 1809-1871 (179 p. typescript), including techniques for painting portraits, ingredients for colors, care and preservation of paintings, criticisms of other artists and explanations of their paintings and techniques; and a journal, 1792-1793 and 1799-1846 (1 v., 301 p. typescript).</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <altformavail id="aspace_hzc212408n530as09959774492348">
